  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bilateral discussion on US support in tackling economic challenges",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Sri Lankan-US bilateral discussion has taken place on the potential areas of US support in tackling the many challenges posed by the country's economic crisis.",
        "The meeting was held on Tuesday (28) in connection with a meeting between Robert Cabrot, Under Secretary of State for the Treasury of Asia and senior officials representing the US Treasury and State Department, led by Deputy Secretary of State for South and Central Asia Kelly Geiterling, and Foreign Secretary Aruni Wijewardene.",
        "Foreign Secretary Wijewardene welcomed the strong and diversified bilateral partnership between the two countries which is mutually beneficial and contributes towards the well-being of the people of Sri Lanka.",
        "The meeting was also attended by US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sung and officials from the US Treasury Department, the US Embassy and the US Embassy in Colombo."
      ],
